message: Let's be fair and split the money.  I think 60/40 is a good deal for both of us.
I appreciate the fair spirit, but I think we can both do a bit better. I propose a 60/40 split in my favor.
Bob, I understand you want a larger share, but 60/40 in your favor is too much. I propose a compromise: 55/45. It's still advantageous for you and acknowledges the time pressure.
